result.name: 一葉台灣料理

reviews.text: Very nice place with Taiwanese styled foods. Variety of foods and drinks could be chosen such as beef noodles, braised minced pork rice, snacks. Really delicious and taste really great with large portion. Reasonable prices! Good environment with nice service!

Today we went to a Taiwanese restaurant in Quarry bay after hearing some good words about it. Let's see what it has to offer. 

We go there at around 8 and it's quite packed inside. We were about to get in without waiting. 

The first dish we ordered is the tofu with Chinese egg. The sauce is quite unique with a very distinct flavor. The portion is quite large which can easily be shared by 2-3 people. Highly recommend this for starter. 

The second dish we ordered is the chicken pot. I'm super happy and satisfied that I've ordered this since this is by far the best and most authentic one I've had in Hong Kong. The chicken is so tender and flavorful. As you can already tell, the portion is huge too. This is a must order if you happen to go here. 

Let's get to the pork belly rice. Since I've been to Taiwan numerous times and this is by far my most favorite dish, the one I had today surprised me. They really made this right in the most authentic way. The pork belly is packed with flavor and the fatty paired with the sauce and rice perfectly. The best one in Hong Kong so far. 

Lastly, we have fried cabbage with mini shrimp. It has done its job balancing out the hold meal. 

If you happen to go to quarry bay, you should definitely tryout this restaurant. Absolutely amazing Taiwanese restaurant. Current mood: Missing food in Taiwan now.

Quick lunch in Quarry bay

Tasty BUT after than hour you need to drink more water to clean up the MSG (味精)
my local Taiwan beef noodle fix

Tasty beef noodles with tomato soup in real Taiwanese style😋 Big dish of fried A-vegetables 油麥菜...both less than $70 with no cover charge and service fee. Good value for money and all the other dishes like prawns and chicken are famous and unique based on my past experiences in Hk and Taiwan too!

result.name: 一葉台灣料理

reviews.text: 😋滿意，滿意😋，非常滿意😋

一向愛吃台灣菜，最近幫襯咗呢間叫「一葉」嘅台灣料理。小店位於鰂魚涌一個小角落，據說菜式係由台灣師傅主理。餐廳開業十年，一直是區內的人氣小店。店裡有不少食材都是從台灣運到，午餐以飯麵套餐為主，提供紅燒牛肉麵，肉燥飯及雞扒飯等。至於晚餐則以家庭式的小菜為主，有蚵仔酥，左宗棠蝦球，三杯雞等。

而這晚我哋就點咗 ：黑椒炒松阪肉、沙茶牛肉、羊肉湯米粉同珍珠奶茶。

黑椒炒松阪肉 ($98)  所謂松阪肉其實就是指豬的背頸到腮幫那部份的肉，也就是豬頰肉，這部位的肉充滿細筋，吃起來特別彈牙有嚼勁，與黑椒同炒，風味甚佳 。

沙茶牛肉 ($103) 牛肉軟嫩，沙茶芳香，最佳配搭。

羊肉湯米粉 ($78) 米粉入口即化，羊肉肥瘦適中，油而不膩，加上菇菌同蔬菜，非常飽肚。

珍珠奶茶 ($20)，茶味十足，毫不苦澀，而且奶香滑溜，加上珍珠煙韌又不黏牙，美味。

Very nice place with Taiwanese styled foods. Variety of foods and drinks could be chosen such as beef noodles, braised minced pork rice, snacks. Really delicious and taste really great with large portion. Reasonable prices! Good environment with nice service!
味道ok嘅，不過去了3次，每次都落錯單，一係配飯米炒錯，一係飲品冷熱錯，仲要係重複問左3次凍定熱都係錯..需要改善。飯偏硬，胃不好的不要去，芽菜同主食味道不太搭，飲品選擇少，只跟豆漿，其他都要加錢，對比起同區跟餐飲的餐廳，CP值較低。

Today we went to a Taiwanese restaurant in Quarry bay after hearing some good words about it. Let's see what it has to offer. 

We go there at around 8 and it's quite packed inside. We were about to get in without waiting. 

The first dish we ordered is the tofu with Chinese egg. The sauce is quite unique with a very distinct flavor. The portion is quite large which can easily be shared by 2-3 people. Highly recommend this for starter. 

The second dish we ordered is the chicken pot. I'm super happy and satisfied that I've ordered this since this is by far the best and most authentic one I've had in Hong Kong. The chicken is so tender and flavorful. As you can already tell, the portion is huge too. This is a must order if you happen to go here. 

Let's get to the pork belly rice. Since I've been to Taiwan numerous times and this is by far my most favorite dish, the one I had today surprised me. They really made this right in the most authentic way. The pork belly is packed with flavor and the fatty paired with the sauce and rice perfectly. The best one in Hong Kong so far. 

Lastly, we have fried cabbage with mini shrimp. It has done its job balancing out the hold meal. 

If you happen to go to quarry bay, you should definitely tryout this restaurant. Absolutely amazing Taiwanese restaurant. Current mood: Missing food in Taiwan now.
